name: WARPLINES - hy[103]xTr.scoppe
description:
WARPLINES is an digital art experiment using video and audio synthesis, using a series of analog pedals to create a sum of sound waves, finalized with a BOSS compressor to normalize the track. The video synthesis was for programmed in HTML and put together with a generative code to give randomness to the pattern. This is a 3 part collection which is for FREE. All remainds copys gonna be burned at 27/09/2021.

-WAV 48kHz 24 bits depth
-MP4 3000p X 3000p 25 FPS
